#

Creamy Seafood Pasta

30 min
$15
800 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

SeafoodHigh ProteinNut Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

PastaSeafoodCreamyQuick Meal

Description

A rich and creamy dish featuring fresh seafood and perfectly cooked pasta, ideal for a comforting yet elegant meal.

Ingredients

  • fettuccine pasta: 8 ounces
  • shrimp, peeled and deveined: 1 cup
  • scallops: 1 cup
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • parmesan cheese, grated: 1/2 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh parsley, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
